氛，雖有多個由長者及大媽把守的鄭泳舜街站，但大多戰意甚低，播着鄭的選情告急聲帶吃喝聊天，閒時只派一、兩張選舉單張，情況與2015年11月區選馮檢基大戰陳穎欣時的熾熱氣氛不同。<br />\n<br />\n昨天所見區內近乎所有宣傳品也屬鄭泳舜，姚松炎只有一、兩張被破壞的海報和橫額，麗閣票站昨午投票率亦較大選時為低。<br />\n本報昨多次致電馮檢基但未獲回覆。有民主派指馮檢基昨午曾到石硤尾為姚松炎拉票。馮檢基初選期間曾透過facebook不斷為自己拉票，而前日的帖文呼籲選民3.11投票時，只稱支持民主派，隻字不提姚松炎。<br />\n<br />\n同樣在泛民初選輸給姚松炎的民主黨袁海文則擔任姚的監察投票代理人，全日把守西九四小龍票站，留意投票人數增長。<br />\n■記者許偉賢"},{"pid":"5152b60f0c771816e2cbef06a802095dfe6e1170","tid":589284,"uid":131245,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0dfe3cb1f4a529f19aa3cb98eff9e306fed25949","tid":589284,"uid":20048,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ba0ecde4d7e8c42f384e8afd7ba850f76a072e58","tid":589284,"uid":131245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"06b18481c060d1c1da1bac9941c0044e3e84f5a0","tid":589284,"uid":54629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T22:31:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T22:34:57.000Z","msg":"會唔會係人哋唔鍾意左膠？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T22:42:34.000Z","msg":"其實建制呢幾年都用左好心機搞鳩泛民票倉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T22:46:51.000Z","msg":"咁左膠本身有冇錯先？唔好理人哋住"},{"pid":"9472f32a106034a5ae947dc9c2e0cece9f5042db","tid":589284,"uid":64874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2f88f205cdcd088340eabe7ad20311410148696","tid":589284,"uid":66784,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T22:44:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180312/20329143\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180312%2F20329143&d=55tMRWADLO9ucYr%2BwAffSwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=9a2eb4b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180312%2F20329143&h=7c6f74dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180312/2032914