65f4433d5c23b315c73eb237fd541ce0332ca0","tid":589284,"uid":21392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01e29a08d24fd58f22f350802f168a82cb70a1c2","tid":589284,"uid":133130,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T22:27:02.000Z","msg":"以2016年立法會選舉結果計算，九龍西的大坑西邨、大坑東邨、南山苑、仁寶大廈的票站，由民協譚國僑擔任區議員，是民主派在立法會九西的最大票倉，可是姚松炎敗於鄭泳舜手下。<br />\n<br />\n過去民主派在這一區的得票達67%。但鄭泳舜攻下這個民主派橋頭堡，鄭奪得51%得票，姚松炎只獲48%，即這票站民主派的得票率下跌19個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n民協馮檢基老巢深水埗麗閣亦不保，姚松炎只獲48%，鄭則獲50%。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:23:31.000Z","msg":"含撚派又睇唔到到底輸邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n姚生係啟德個邊連一個正式嘅街站都冇<br />\n根本已經知輸硬呢區唔放咁多人落去<br />\n成班弱智含撚派就去攻擊呢點<br />\n笑撚死人，得閒出下街行下各選區先出黎柒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n含撚派打手唔好淨係摺埋自己係屋企含撚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88bbf9b7337c2be21f323b32007fc5c385eaf178","tid":589284,"uid":85911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:26:16.000Z","msg":"講真如果係基哥選好大機會拎得返呢一席<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 起碼會有呀婆投佢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7113249ba33b5d009efe379d04680485310d9f3b","tid":589284,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88bbf9b7337c2be21f323b32007fc5c385eaf178","tid":589284,"uid":85911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:26:16.000Z","msg":"講真如果係基哥選好大機會拎得返呢一席<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgm