以外，加上尋求其他方法，確保泛民補選勝算，他認為這與尊重機制沒有矛盾。他又稱，民主派在17日早上經商討後同意，若姚松炎遭DQ，「支持遞補機制，同時物色一包底人選（Plan D）」。他說，17號晚上民主動力創會召集人鄭宇碩邀請他、姚松炎與馮檢基會面，當時有交流意見。他重申，鄭和自己有對馮檢基清楚表示，「若你去選，民主派同民主動力都會支持你，這決定權放了在馮檢基同民協身上」。<br />\n<br />\nSource :<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180124/s00002/1516731136507\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180124%2Fs00002%2F1516731136507&d=55tMRWADLO9ucYr%2BwAffSwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=003d591e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180124%2Fs00002%2F1516731136507&h=589ff243\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180124/s00002/1516731136507</a>"},{"pid":"87026ceef6f5d35f98a7698f30189b0a413e3135","tid":589284,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b47cf457bda653940812535bad962e42f65d40a","tid":589284,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T13:16:43.000Z","msg":"朱凱廸其後在D100《左右大局》表示，認為馮檢基勝算低，所以他在民主派中帶出討論，在機制以外，加上尋求其他方法，確保泛民補選勝算，他認為這與尊重機制沒有矛盾。他又稱，民主派在17日早上經商討後同意，若姚松炎遭DQ，「支持遞補機制，同時物色一包底人選（Plan D）」。他說，17號晚上民主動力創會召集人鄭宇碩邀請他、姚松炎與馮檢基會面，當時有交流意見。他重申，鄭和自己有對馮檢基清楚表示，「若你去選，民主派同民主動力都會支持你，這決定權放了在馮檢基同民協身上」。<br />\n<br />\nSource :<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180124/s00002/1516731136507\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180124%2Fs00002%2F1516731136507&d=55tMRWADLO9ucYr%2BwAffSwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=003d591e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180124%2Fs00002%2F1516731136507&h=589ff243\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180124/s00002/1516731136507</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T00:34:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkg